<div class="lang-en">
<section id="fire">
  <h2>Fire Element (<span class="chinese-char">火</span>) &mdash; Years Ending in 6 or 7</h2>
  <p><strong>Direction:</strong> South &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Season:</strong> Summer &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Colour:</strong> Red &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Organ:</strong> Heart</p>
  <p>Fire is the element of illumination, passion, and transformation. Fire-element people are <strong>charismatic, enthusiastic, and action-oriented</strong>. They light up rooms, inspire followers, and pursue goals with intensity. 2026 is a Fire year (<span class="chinese-char">丙午</span>), making this element especially prominent.</p>
  <p><strong>Strengths:</strong> Leadership, boldness, joy, clarity of purpose. Fire people are natural performers, entrepreneurs, and motivators. They make decisions quickly and commit fully.</p>
  <p><strong>Challenges:</strong> Impatience, burnout, volatility. Fire burns bright but can consume its fuel. Fire-element people may struggle with sustained effort, emotional regulation, and the patience required for long-term projects.</p>
  <p><strong>Example:</strong> A Fire Horse (2026) doubles the Fire energy &mdash; the Horse already carries intrinsic Fire. This combination creates exceptional dynamism but requires conscious effort to cultivate stillness and balance.</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-tc">
<section id="fire">
  <h2>火元素（<span class="chinese-char">火</span>）——尾數6或7的年份</h2>
  <p><strong>方位：</strong>南 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>季節：</strong>夏 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>顏色：</strong>紅色 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>臟腑：</strong>心</p>
  <p>火是光明、熱情和變革的元素。火命人<strong>富有魅力、熱忱且行動力強</strong>。他們照亮場合、激勵追隨者、全力以赴地追求目標。2026年為火年（<span class="chinese-char">丙午</span>），此元素尤為突出。</p>
  <p><strong>優勢：</strong>領導力、魄力、喜樂、目標明確。火命人是天生的表演者、創業家和激勵者。他們決策迅速、全心投入。</p>
  <p><strong>挑戰：</strong>急躁、倦怠、情緒波動。火焰雖明亮卻會耗盡燃料。火命人可能在持續努力、情緒管理及長期項目所需的耐心方面遇到困難。</p>
  <p><strong>舉例：</strong>火馬（2026年）使火氣加倍——馬本身就帶有內在火元素。這種組合產生非凡的活力，但需要有意識地培養靜定與平衡。</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-sc">
<section id="fire">
  <h2>火元素（<span class="chinese-char">火</span>）——尾数6或7的年份</h2>
  <p><strong>方位：</strong>南 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>季节：</strong>夏 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>颜色：</strong>红色 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>脏腑：</strong>心</p>
  <p>火是光明、热情和变革的元素。火命人<strong>富有魅力、热忱且行动力强</strong>。他们照亮场合、激励追随者、全力以赴地追求目标。2026年为火年（<span class="chinese-char">丙午</span>），此元素尤为突出。</p>
  <p><strong>优势：</strong>领导力、魄力、喜乐、目标明确。火命人是天生的表演者、创业家和激励者。他们决策迅速、全心投入。</p>
  <p><strong>挑战：</strong>急躁、倦怠、情绪波动。火焰虽明亮却会耗尽燃料。火命人可能在持续努力、情绪管理及长期项目所需的耐心方面遇到困难。</p>
  <p><strong>举例：</strong>火马（2026年）使火气加倍——马本身就带有内在火元素。这种组合产生非凡的活力，但需要有意识地培养静定与平衡。</p>
</section>
</div>

<div class="lang-en">
<section id="earth">
  <h2>Earth Element (<span class="chinese-char">土</span>) &mdash; Years Ending in 8 or 9</h2>
  <p><strong>Direction:</strong> Centre &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Season:</strong> Late Summer &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Colour:</strong> Yellow/Brown &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Organ:</strong> Spleen/Stomach</p>
  <p>Earth is the stabilising force at the centre of the Wu Xing cycle. Earth-element people are <strong>grounded, reliable, and methodical</strong>. They value security, build structures that endure, and provide stability for those around them.</p>
  <p><strong>Strengths:</strong> Dependability, patience, practical wisdom, loyalty. Earth people excel in management, finance, agriculture, and any field requiring steady accumulation over time.</p>
  <p><strong>Challenges:</strong> Rigidity, over-caution, possessiveness. Earth's desire for security can become hoarding &mdash; of resources, relationships, or outdated ideas. Earth-element people may resist necessary change.</p>
  <p><strong>Example:</strong> An Earth Dragon (1988) tempers the Dragon's ambition with Earth's pragmatism. The result is a person who dreams big but builds methodically &mdash; less flashy than a Fire Dragon but often more successful in the long run.</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-tc">
<section id="earth">
  <h2>土元素（<span class="chinese-char">土</span>）——尾數8或9的年份</h2>
  <p><strong>方位：</strong>中央 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>季節：</strong>長夏 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>顏色：</strong>黃色/棕色 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>臟腑：</strong>脾/胃</p>
  <p>土是五行循環中居於中央的穩定力量。土命人<strong>踏實、可靠且有條理</strong>。他們重視安全感，建造經久不衰的架構，為周圍的人提供穩定。</p>
  <p><strong>優勢：</strong>可靠、耐心、實際智慧、忠誠。土命人擅長管理、金融、農業以及任何需要長期穩步積累的領域。</p>
  <p><strong>挑戰：</strong>固執、過度謹慎、佔有欲。土對安全感的渴望可能演變為囤積——無論是資源、關係還是過時的觀念。土命人可能抗拒必要的變革。</p>
  <p><strong>舉例：</strong>土龍（1988年）以土的務實調和龍的雄心。其結果是一個胸懷大志卻步步為營的人——不如火龍耀眼，但長遠來看往往更為成功。</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-sc">
<section id="earth">
  <h2>土元素（<span class="chinese-char">土</span>）——尾数8或9的年份</h2>
  <p><strong>方位：</strong>中央 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>季节：</strong>长夏 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>颜色：</strong>黄色/棕色 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>脏腑：</strong>脾/胃</p>
  <p>土是五行循环中居于中央的稳定力量。土命人<strong>踏实、可靠且有条理</strong>。他们重视安全感，建造经久不衰的架构，为周围的人提供稳定。</p>
  <p><strong>优势：</strong>可靠、耐心、实际智慧、忠诚。土命人擅长管理、金融、农业以及任何需要长期稳步积累的领域。</p>
  <p><strong>挑战：</strong>固执、过度谨慎、占有欲。土对安全感的渴望可能演变为囤积——无论是资源、关系还是过时的观念。土命人可能抗拒必要的变革。</p>
  <p><strong>举例：</strong>土龙（1988年）以土的务实调和龙的雄心。其结果是一个胸怀大志却步步为营的人——不如火龙耀眼，但长远来看往往更为成功。</p>
</section>
</div>

<div class="lang-en">
<section id="metal">
  <h2>Metal Element (<span class="chinese-char">金</span>) &mdash; Years Ending in 0 or 1</h2>
  <p><strong>Direction:</strong> West &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Season:</strong> Autumn &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Colour:</strong> White/Gold &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Organ:</strong> Lungs</p>
  <p>Metal represents precision, refinement, and cutting clarity. Metal-element people are <strong>disciplined, principled, and achievement-driven</strong>. They set high standards for themselves and others, and they possess a natural authority that commands respect.</p>
  <p><strong>Strengths:</strong> Focus, integrity, determination, aesthetic sense. Metal people excel in law, engineering, craftsmanship, and leadership roles requiring decisive judgement.</p>
  <p><strong>Challenges:</strong> Inflexibility, harshness, perfectionism. Metal's sharpness can wound &mdash; these individuals may be overly critical, unforgiving of mistakes, or unable to compromise. Under stress, Metal becomes brittle rather than strong.</p>
  <p><strong>Example:</strong> A Metal Monkey (1980, 2040) combines the Monkey's cleverness with Metal's discipline, creating a person who is both innovative and systematic &mdash; a strategist who executes with precision.</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-tc">
<section id="metal">
  <h2>金元素（<span class="chinese-char">金</span>）——尾數0或1的年份</h2>
  <p><strong>方位：</strong>西 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>季節：</strong>秋 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>顏色：</strong>白色/金色 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>臟腑：</strong>肺</p>
  <p>金代表精準、提煉和銳利的清晰。金命人<strong>自律、有原則且追求成就</strong>。他們對自己和他人都設立高標準，擁有令人敬服的天生權威感。</p>
  <p><strong>優勢：</strong>專注、正直、堅毅、審美品味。金命人擅長法律、工程、工藝以及需要果斷判斷的領導崗位。</p>
  <p><strong>挑戰：</strong>不靈活、嚴厲、完美主義。金的鋒利可能傷人——這類人可能過於挑剔、對錯誤不寬容、或無法妥協。壓力之下，金會變得脆弱而非堅強。</p>
  <p><strong>舉例：</strong>金猴（1980年、2040年）將猴的聰明與金的紀律結合，形成一個既創新又有系統的人——一位精準執行的策略家。</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-sc">
<section id="metal">
  <h2>金元素（<span class="chinese-char">金</span>）——尾数0或1的年份</h2>
  <p><strong>方位：</strong>西 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>季节：</strong>秋 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>颜色：</strong>白色/金色 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>脏腑：</strong>肺</p>
  <p>金代表精准、提炼和锐利的清晰。金命人<strong>自律、有原则且追求成就</strong>。他们对自己和他人都设立高标准，拥有令人敬服的天生权威感。</p>
  <p><strong>优势：</strong>专注、正直、坚毅、审美品味。金命人擅长法律、工程、工艺以及需要果断判断的领导岗位。</p>
  <p><strong>挑战：</strong>不灵活、严厉、完美主义。金的锋利可能伤人——这类人可能过于挑剔、对错误不宽容、或无法妥协。压力之下，金会变得脆弱而非坚强。</p>
  <p><strong>举例：</strong>金猴（1980年、2040年）将猴的聪明与金的纪律结合，形成一个既创新又有系统的人——一位精准执行的策略家。</p>
</section>
</div>

<div class="lang-en">
<section id="water">
  <h2>Water Element (<span class="chinese-char">水</span>) &mdash; Years Ending in 2 or 3</h2>
  <p><strong>Direction:</strong> North &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Season:</strong> Winter &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Colour:</strong> Black/Dark Blue &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Organ:</strong> Kidneys</p>
  <p>Water is the element of wisdom, depth, and adaptability. Water-element people are <strong>intuitive, diplomatic, and perceptive</strong>. Like water itself, they find the path of least resistance and adapt their shape to any container &mdash; they are natural negotiators and communicators.</p>
  <p><strong>Strengths:</strong> Intelligence, empathy, resourcefulness, persuasion. Water people excel in diplomacy, counselling, writing, research, and any field requiring deep understanding of human nature.</p>
  <p><strong>Challenges:</strong> Indecision, anxiety, emotional overwhelm. Water's sensitivity can become a liability &mdash; absorbing others' problems, overthinking, or avoiding confrontation when it is necessary. Under stress, Water becomes stagnant rather than flowing.</p>
  <p><strong>Example:</strong> A Water Tiger (2022) softens the Tiger's aggression with Water's diplomacy, producing a person who is courageous yet tactful &mdash; a leader who persuades rather than commands.</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-tc">
<section id="water">
  <h2>水元素（<span class="chinese-char">水</span>）——尾數2或3的年份</h2>
  <p><strong>方位：</strong>北 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>季節：</strong>冬 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>顏色：</strong>黑色/深藍 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>臟腑：</strong>腎</p>
  <p>水是智慧、深度和適應力的元素。水命人<strong>直覺敏銳、善於外交且洞察力強</strong>。如同水本身，他們尋找阻力最小的路徑，隨容器改變形狀——他們是天生的談判者和溝通者。</p>
  <p><strong>優勢：</strong>聰慧、同理心、足智多謀、說服力。水命人擅長外交、諮詢、寫作、研究以及任何需要深刻理解人性的領域。</p>
  <p><strong>挑戰：</strong>猶豫不決、焦慮、情緒過載。水的敏感可能成為負擔——吸收他人的問題、過度思考、或在必要時迴避衝突。壓力之下，水會變得停滯而非流動。</p>
  <p><strong>舉例：</strong>水虎（2022年）以水的外交才能柔化虎的攻擊性，形成一個勇敢而圓融的人——一位以說服而非命令來領導的領袖。</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-sc">
<section id="water">
  <h2>水元素（<span class="chinese-char">水</span>）——尾数2或3的年份</h2>
  <p><strong>方位：</strong>北 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>季节：</strong>冬 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>颜色：</strong>黑色/深蓝 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>脏腑：</strong>肾</p>
  <p>水是智慧、深度和适应力的元素。水命人<strong>直觉敏锐、善于外交且洞察力强</strong>。如同水本身，他们寻找阻力最小的路径，随容器改变形状——他们是天生的谈判者和沟通者。</p>
  <p><strong>优势：</strong>聪慧、同理心、足智多谋、说服力。水命人擅长外交、咨询、写作、研究以及任何需要深刻理解人性的领域。</p>
  <p><strong>挑战：</strong>犹豫不决、焦虑、情绪过载。水的敏感可能成为负担——吸收他人的问题、过度思考、或在必要时回避冲突。压力之下，水会变得停滞而非流动。</p>
  <p><strong>举例：</strong>水虎（2022年）以水的外交才能柔化虎的攻击性，形成一个勇敢而圆融的人——一位以说服而非命令来领导的领袖。</p>
</section>
</div>

